track_notes: Walked in virgin snow in Jan 2015. No visibility. We used the excellent access track on the Coed Morgannwg Way LDP which has been spoiled by deep ruts in the early part by the 4X4 brigade...If you park where we did be careful walking up the road. You would be just as well parking at the viewpoint at 927031...
track_title: Parked in wide access track entrance to new wind farm
